[@Cucurbit chlorotic yellows virus#Virus*] ([$CCYV#Virus*]), a [@whitefly-transmitted virus#Virus*], is a new member of the [$Crinivirus genus#Virus*], that causes major economic losses in [$cucumber#Plant*], [$melon#Plant*] and [$watermelon#Plant*] [$crops#Plant*].
