[$CCYV#Virus*] in extracts from infected plants was also readily detected by double antibody sandwich [$enzyme-linked immunosorbent assay#Method*] with high sensitivity and specificity.
A [$tissue blot immunoassay#Method*] indicated that [$CCYV#Virus*] localizes in the phloem tissues of the petiole and is distributed in tiny spots within the leaf lamina.
